Title: Gold Plated 925 Sterling Silver Sleeping Cat Necklace Pet Lover Pendant for Women Handmade Polymer Clay Handcrafted Animal Jewelry
Body (HTML): An ancient technique remastered into everyday jewelry Millefiori, originally a glass-work technique used to produce special decorative patterns on glass, has been adapted to create extraordinary and unique patterns manually hand-rolled from polymer clay. Each pattern takes about a week to createNo two patterns are ever exactly the sameOnly the finest precious metal is used to encase the unique polymer clay Fun Fact 1: 'Millefiori' literally translates to '1000 flowers' in Italian Fun Fact 2: Look out for our 'multi-colored' color options to see millefiori transformed into beautiful pieces of jewelry for anyone to enjoy. Enchanting handmade gold plated silver cat necklace pendant beautifully perched along the chain while taking one of its many daily naps!. Exquisitely handcrafted, the loving pet cat pendant measures 0.9x0.5 inches and is threaded through a sturdy, gold filled chain, 16.5 inches designed to gracefully rest just below the lines of the collar bones of the wearer.. Symbolizing grace, agility, and independence, cats are awesome, so what better homage then to adorn your furry friend close to your heart.. The unique feline is made using a remastered ancient millefiori technique adapted to create incredible fine polymer clay jewelry by hand and is available in a bright array of colorful patterns. The adorable cat pendant takes about a week to create by manually molding the polymer clay patterns before setting the design in the precious metal.. Finished with a coating of transparent enamel to ensure it remains as pristine as the moment you set eyes on the piece.. Transform yours or her look with beautiful, inspirational, colorful jewelry. A perfect gift idea, sure to leave a timeless and lasting impression on any special woman who loves her pet cat or any animal lover, whether it be your wife, girlfriend, daughter, sister, mother or that awesome neighbor who feeds all the street cats! A love for animals knows no age, this elegant and lovely cat necklace is designed for all, young and old.
